			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 style="text-align: left;">Announcing:</h2>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">In order to edify our ministry partners around the world, and to report on the great outpouring of the Holy Spirit that is taking place, we have launched:</h3>
<h1 style="text-align: center;"><em>Outpouring!</em></h1>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img title="overflow-1.jpg" src="http://brothermel.podbean.com/mf/web/cten6s/overflow-1.jpg" border="0" alt="overflow-1.jpg" width="345" height="461" /></p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">The new online magazine of</h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Mel Montgomery Ministries International</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;">
</p><p style="text-align: left;"><strong><em>Outpouring!</em></strong> is a free online magazine we send out by e-mail each month.</p>
<p align="left"><strong><em>Outpouring!</em></strong> helps  you to step over into the present-day outpouring of the Holy Spirit  that is setting individuals and churches ablaze with the Holy Ghost and  Fire.</p>
<p align="left"><strong><em>Outpouring!</em></strong> presents to you the latest rare recordings by the faith giants of old that have just been uploaded to Mel Montgomery Ministries International&#8217;s website:  <span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong><a href="http://www.brothermel.com" target="_blank">www.brothermel.com</a></strong></span>.</p>
<p align="left"><strong><em>Outpouring!</em></strong> features new recordings and teaching articles by Brother Mel in which  he shares with you fresh truths that the Holy Spirit is emphasizing  today.</p>
<p align="left"><strong><em>Outpouring!</em></strong> announces Brother Mel&#8217;s itinerary to our partners around the world so that you cna know when he will be holding a &#8220;Holy Ghost and Fire&#8221; meeting near you.</p>
<p align="left"><strong><em>Outpouring!</em></strong> will stir your faith, instruct you, and help you to reach up to God for fresh fire.</p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">To subscribe to this free monthly e-mail, <span style="color: #0000ff;"><a href="http://www.brothermel.com/guestbook.aspx" target="_blank">please click here</a></span>.</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;">.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">.</p>
