Brother Mel preached the this message at the opening service of the H.I.M. Annual Ministers Convention.  He began by describing to the assembled ministers aspects of the current Great Awakening that is in the earth, and comparing it with previous moves of God.  He told about two of the three recent angelic visitations he had experienced, and what he believed they meant.

Then he launched into a message in which he confronted, and comforted, the listeners by warning and exhorting them to learn from the moves of the past, and the mistakes thereof, so that they do not sit out the current move.  He spoke about two of the three biblical truths that had been emphasized to him by the Lord since the angelic visitations.

Brother Mel concluded by describing a vision the Lord gave him years ago of a powerful evil spirit that works against Christians, hindering them from receiving from God.  He concluded by sharing a testimony of personal revival and breakthrough, and invited ministers to come forward to seek the Lord, and to be prayed for to receive newness in God.  Many ministers came forward, and the recording includes the time of personal ministry, prayer, and the operation of spiritual gifts.

Mel reports that the Lord ministered deeply to fellow ministers, saying that as he preached, "I could see psychological, mental, and spiritual loads visibly lift off of various ministers, and their countenances brightened like the difference between night and day."

