<h3 style="text-align: center;">Rev. Mel C. Montgomery</h3>
<h3>Some Christians believe that they are beginning to see the first stirrings of a new move of God, even perhaps, a new &#8220;Great Awakening&#8221; akin to what visited our land in the 1700s and 1800s.</h3>
<h3>In this podcast series, Rev. Mel Montgomery teaches about the First and Second Great Awakenings, drawing parallels between what happened then and what is happening now.</h3>
<h3>Brother Mel also describes and explains in detail three angelic visitations he received in late 2009 and early 2010.</h3>
<h3>He concludes by sharing three directions the Lord has given him, which will help individuals and ministries enter into this new flow from Heaven.</h3>
