<p align="left"><strong> </strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: small;">The term &#8220;Awakening&#8221; has  emerged in recent Charismatic teachings.  The First Great Awakening (1740 -  1750) changed the course of our nation.  We examine characteristics of the Great  Awakenings of the past and identify parallels with the current move of God.  In  this podcast, the Holy Spirit inspires a message in tongues and provides the  interpretation.</span></p>
